com.upsight.android.internal.logger

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.upsight.android.internal.logger.Logger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UpsightLogger

    public final class Logger
extends java.lang.Object
implements UpsightLogger
    UpsightLogger is a convenience class for logging information in the Upsight data store. This logs can then be subscribed to and analysed or sent to a server.
